 nJeudi 31 mars 2016 à 19h00 dans l'amphi A de l'ENSEIRB MATMECA\, Stép
 hane NICOLL<a href="http://www.bordeauxjug.org/speakers#mathieuancelin"></
 a>\, viendra nous présenter Spring Boot.\nSpring Boot\, the new conventio
 n-over-configuration centric framework from the Spring team at Pivotal\, m
 arries Spring's flexibility with conventional\, common sense defaults to m
 ake application development move swiftly and enjoyable.\nIt's ideally suit
 ed for building microservices and distributed systems and makes streamlini
 ng devops practices simple.\nJoin Spring Boot committer Stéphane Nicoll f
 or a look at what Spring Boot is\, why it's turning heads\, why you should
