 📍 ENSEIRB\, 1 Avenue du Docteur Albert Schweitzer\, Talence\, France\n\
 nIn this session Antonio will introduce Context & Dependency Injection\, e
 xplain most of the concepts (injection\, producers\, interceptors\, decora
 tors\, events...) but also show you why CDI has become the main specificat
 ion of Java EE. As CDI 2.0 is in the starting block\, Antonio\, who is par
