BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Club de lecture 24.2 - Agile conversations
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Paris:20240210T100000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Paris:20240210T120000
UID:https://www.meetup.com/agile-bordeaux/events/297716202/@community-even
 ts
DESCRIPTION:🔗 https://www.meetup.com/agile-bordeaux/events/297716202/\n
 📍 Le Node - Aquinum\, 12 Rue des Faussets\, Bordeaux\, France\n\n**Le c
 lub de lecture 24.2 se tiendra samedi 10 février de 10h00 à 12h00 au Nod
 e.**\n**Le livre sélectionné est “Agile conversations” de Douglas Sq
 uirrel et Jeffrey Fredrick.**\n“Today\, software organizations are trans
 forming the way work gets done through practices like Agile\, Lean\, and D
 evOps. But as commonly implemented as these methods are\, many transformat
 ions still fail\, largely because the organization misses a critical step:
  culture and how people communicate. Agile Conversations brings an updated
 \, practical\, step-by-step guide to using the power of conversation to bu
 ild effective\, high-performing teams to achieve truly Agile results. To a
 dvance your organization's transformation\, learn how to have productive c
 onversations that overcome cognitive bias and fear. Consultants Douglas Sq
 uirrel and Jeffrey Fredrick show readers how to utilize the Five Conversat
 ions to help teams build trust\, alleviate fear\, answer the "whys\," defi
 ne commitments\, and hold everyone accountable. These five conversations g
 ive teams everything they need to reach peak performance\, and they are ex
 actly what's missing from too many teams today. Stop focusing just on proc
 esses and practices that leave your organization stuck with culture-less r
 ituals. Instead\, unleash the unique human power of conversation.”\n\\*\
 \*\\*\\*\\*\nLe club de lecture est un moment de partage et d’échange a
 utour d’un livre.Les participants ont lu l’ouvrage ou tout au moins un
 e partie significative.\nLe nombre de places étant limité\, merci de vou
 s désinscrire si vous ne pouvez plus vous joindre à nous.\n\nCommunauté
 : agile-bordeaux\n👥 13 participant(s)\nLimité à 15 places
LOCATION:Le Node - Aquinum\, 12 Rue des Faussets\, Bordeaux\, France
TZID:Europe/Paris
URL:https://www.meetup.com/agile-bordeaux/events/297716202/
END:VEVENT
